import React from 'react'

function formSignUp() {
    return (
        <Form>
            <Form.Group controlId="formName">
                <Form.Label>Name</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Enter name" name="username"/>
            </Form.Group>

            <Form.Group controlId="formEmail">
                <Form.Label>Email address</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control type="email" placeholder="Enter email" name="useremail"/>
            </Form.Group>

            <Form.Group controlId="formPassword">
                <Form.Label>Password</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control type="password" placeholder="Password" name="userpass"/>
            </Form.Group>

            <Form.Group controlId="formPasswordConfirm">
                <Form.Label>Confirm Password</Form.Label>
                <Form.Control type="password" placeholder="Confirm Password" name="userpassconf"/>
            </Form.Group>

            <Form.Group controlId="formCheckbox">
                <Form.Check type="checkbox" label="Check me out" />
            </Form.Group>
            <Button variant="primary" type="submit">
                Submit
            </Button>
        </Form>
    )
}

export default formSignUp;
